  "mainText": "Italiano English Reserved Area Contacts Company Pens Customisation Sample kits Finishes Recycled pens More maxema ® via vittime delle foibe 15 10088 volpiano torino italy t +39 011 970 4500 f +39 011 970 4550 maxema@maxema.com P PRODUCTS Our pens Kind / Kind / Icon Pure / Flow Pure / Dot / Zink / Pixel / Bay / Mood Metal / Kind / Mood / Flow / View / Tag Green / Next / Tag / Icon / Icon green / Ethic Search by color rose/purple azure / blue green yellow/orange red cream/brown grey black white select a color S Services customisation packaging pantone colors sample kits C COMPANY Maxema Company contacts FAVORITES SAMPLE KITS ACCOUNT FAQ MEDIA DISCLAIMER previous model/ next model HomePens Catalogue View View decisive personality Technical information Download pdfof this model View expresses a harmonious blend of curved lines and slender sections that evoke prestige and emphasise the value of uniqueness. The value of timeless quality, beauty and practicality, a value that is a resource and stimulus of responsible consumption, the offshoot of a broader and more aware vision.? Available in recycled plastic for orders over 10,000 units. 1/4 Details 2/4 Variants 3/4 Technical information 4/4 Customisations log in P/View 1/4 Details Details of the pen The sleek design of the cap adds elegance and balances the large clip Refined elegance to enhance the prestige of a brand Chromed tip in all versions 2/4 Models and colors Available in 5 models and 66 color variants V1 - C CR Show details add to favorites ABS plastic, glossy finishes, solid colours, chromed tip and clip V1 - 30 CR Show details add to favorites ABS plastic, glossy finishes, transparent colours, chromed tip and clip V1 - AL CR Show details add to favorites ABS plastic, aluminium painting, chromed tip and clip V1 - GOM C CR T Show details add to favorites ABS plastic, solid colours, rubber finish barrel, chromed tip and clip V1 - GOM C CR Show details add to favorites ABS plastic, solid colours, rubber finish barrel, chromed tip and clip 3/4 Technical information Print areas and tech specs Features ● twist action ● made of non-toxic, highly resistent ABS plastic ● metal chrome finish clip available for laser engraving and pad printing ● galvanic process used to chrome tip ● Jumbo refill, blue and black ink ● available in glossy, rubberised or aluminium painted finish Modularity you can combine differently coloured parts from the same version (or code number), or elements from different versions A clip B cap C barrel Print areas 1 pad printing 40 x 6 mm 2 laser engraving 30 x 7 mm 3 pad printing 47 x 9 mm 4 screen printing 42 x 30 mm 4/4 Customisations The brands mentioned in this catalogue are the exclusive property of the respective owners. They are used for purely illustrative purposes and cannot be the object of any buying and selling transactions, under any circumstances. via vittime delle foibe 15 10088 volpiano torino italy t +39 011 970 4500 f +39 011 970 4550 maxema@maxema.com MAXEMA SRL P.IVA 05321380015 privacy policy var acceptText='Accetto'; var policy_url='/cookie_privacy_policy/en'; var cookie_message='Il sito www.maxema.com utilizza cookie esclusivamente tecnici per permettere una corretta navigazione e la completa fruizione di tutti i contenuti da parte dell\\'utente. Non utilizziamo in alcun modo cookie di profilazione.'; var acceptText='I Understand'; var policy_url='/cookie_privacy_policy/en'; var cookie_message='This site uses cookies to improve their services and experience of readers. If you decide to continue browsing we consider that you accept their use.'; $(document).ready(function(){ $.cookieBar({ message: cookie_message, acceptButton: true, acceptText: acceptText, policyButton: true, policyText: 'Privacy Policy', policyURL: policy_url, autoEnable: true, acceptOnContinue: false, acceptOnScroll: false, acceptAnyClick: false, expireDays: 365, renewOnVisit: false, forceShow: false, bottom:true, fixed:true, domain: 'www.maxema.com', ref